v0.3
----
DONE
- add of a service button
- smoother rendering
- stability improved
- roms sorted by long name
- remove roms bios from listing (neogeo, pgm, ... ?)
- improved megadrive & pcengine support. Roms required prefix (md_, pce_, tg_, sgx_)
BUGS FIXED
- iOS 4.x compatible
- wrong screen rotation

